<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL23">
<l>kaṅkaiyiṟ puṉita māya kāviri naṭuvu pāṭṭup</l>
<l>poṅkunīr parantu pāyum pūmpoḻi laraṅkan taṉṉu</l>
<l>ḷeṅkaṇmā liṟaiva ṉīcaṉ kiṭantatōr kiṭakkai kaṇṭu</l>
<l>meṅṅaṉa maṟantu vāḻkē ṉēḻaiyē ṉēḻai yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even after seeing the posture in which our Māl, God, the Supreme Being</l>
<l>reclines inside Raṅgam with flower groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where gushing water flows spreading [everywhere],</l>
<l>in the middle of the Kāverī that is holier than the Ganges,</l>
<l>How can I—wretched I—live on forgetting [Him]. I am a wretched one!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
